| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0410 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5172a722-de24-5ad2-9587-6bc73b51ac33"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
